Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.56,0:01:31.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,悲惨的新一天又悲惨地开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.56,0:01:31.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Another miserable start to another miserable day
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.61,0:01:34.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.61,0:01:34.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Greetings
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.45,0:01:38.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一看就身心健康  胸怀幽默
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.45,0:01:38.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You strike me as a man with a healthy sense of humor
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.03,0:01:42.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小子  我有优惠要给你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.03,0:01:42.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, boy, do I have just the offer for you
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.74,0:01:44.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,保证实惠到可以让你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.74,0:01:44.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a deal you can really sink
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.83,0:01:46.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咬牙切齿狠狠投入
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.83,0:01:46.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,your chattering teeth into
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.25,0:01:48.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还不止呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.25,0:01:48.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But that's not all
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.21,0:01:50.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喜不喜欢咬口香糖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.21,0:01:50.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you like to snap your gum?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.17,0:01:51.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个口香糖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.17,0:01:51.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well this gum
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.71,0:01:53.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以咬你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.71,0:01:53.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,snaps you
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.42,0:01:56.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想把无价小道具带回家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.42,0:01:56.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These priceless gags can be yours
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.63,0:01:59.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要二十四块九毛九的低价
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.63,0:01:59.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for the low, low price of 24.99
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.76,0:02:00.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过现在购买
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.76,0:02:00.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But if you act now
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.85,0:02:05.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还能额外赠送一套牛排刀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.85,0:02:05.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll throw in a free set of steak knives
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.31,0:02:12.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你闹够了没  爸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.31,0:02:12.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you finished now, Dad?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.15,0:02:17.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么认出来是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.15,0:02:17.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How did you know it was me?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.36,0:02:19.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,带我进去坐坐吧  儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.36,0:02:19.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bring it in, son
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.61,0:02:22.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我新定了条推销路线  刚飞来这
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.61,0:02:22.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just flew into town on my new sales route
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.87,0:02:25.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就想到顺路来看看你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.87,0:02:25.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and thought I would drop by
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.20,0:02:27.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,顺便考虑要在这暂留几天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.20,0:02:27.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And also thought I would stay for a few days
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.87,0:02:28.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.87,0:02:28.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You--
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.12,0:02:28.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.12,0:02:28.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.21,0:02:37.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真了不起  小章
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.21,0:02:37.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Very impressive, Squiddy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.97,0:02:39.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你真这么觉得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.97,0:02:39.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You really think so?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.59,0:02:40.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.59,0:02:40.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.89,0:02:42.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就爱看小丑画
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.89,0:02:42.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love clown paintings
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.18,0:02:45.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开心点嘛  儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.18,0:02:45.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cheer up, son
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.97,0:02:46.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不你给我吹首
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.97,0:02:46.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't you play me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.93,0:02:49.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你那特好听的竖笛曲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.93,0:02:49.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,one of your famous clarinet tunes?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.56,0:02:52.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我最近确实在练新曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.56,0:02:52.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I have been practicing a new song
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.98,0:03:00.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是经典款吹泡泡竖笛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.98,0:03:00.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the classic bubble-blowing clarinet
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.03,0:03:01.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要六块九毛九
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:01.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's only 6.99
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.74,0:03:07.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这一定会是我这辈子最漫长的几天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.74,0:03:07.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This will be the longest few days of my life
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.25,0:03:13.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.25,0:03:13.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dad
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.96,0:03:16.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你喇叭就不能小点声吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.96,0:03:16.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can you keep your honking down?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.46,0:03:18.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:18.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.30,0:03:23.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是你们喜欢尖叫鸡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.30,0:03:23.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you like rubber chickens
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.01,0:03:25.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就肯定会爱上这自行车喇叭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.01,0:03:25.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you'll love this bicycle horn
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.18,0:03:28.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  小子们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.18,0:03:28.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.73,0:03:30.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这儿的喇叭多得是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.73,0:03:30.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got horns-a-plenty
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.44,0:03:31.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,雾号
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.44,0:03:31.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fog horns
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.90,0:03:34.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,法国圆号
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:34.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,French horns
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.07,0:03:37.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大喇叭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.07,0:03:37.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bull horns
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.07,0:03:37.61,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(892,920)}牛
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.65,0:03:41.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都只要九块九毛九
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:41.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just 9.99 each
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.78,0:03:43.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,主流的信用卡我都收哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.78,0:03:43.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I take all major credit cards
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.41,0:03:45.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过这卡我保证会还回去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:45.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I promise, I give them all back
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.54,0:03:50.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托  别给我烦人的邻居
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.54,0:03:50.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, do not arm my annoying neighbors
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.16,0:03:52.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,配备更烦人的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.16,0:03:52.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with even more annoying props
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.67,0:03:54.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我求你了  老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.67,0:03:54.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you, Father
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.83,0:03:56.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.83,0:03:56.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.09,0:03:58.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  他是你爸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:58.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, this is your dad?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.84,0:04:01.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还以为蟹老板是你爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:01.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought Mr. Krabs was your dad
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.88,0:04:03.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.88,0:04:03.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.18,0:04:08.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们别来烦我跟爸  我会不胜感激
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:04.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I would appreciate it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:08.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if you left my father and I alone
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.43,0:04:09.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.43,0:04:09.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.06,0:04:09.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:09.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.81,0:04:10.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.81,0:04:10.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Join in
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.77,0:04:12.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,玩一下又不会受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:12.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's just harmless fun
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.48,0:04:14.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  无伤大雅又好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:14.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, harmless fun
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.60,0:04:16.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,握个手吧  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.60,0:04:16.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Put her there, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.94,0:04:21.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:21.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.20,0:04:25.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:25.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.28,0:04:28.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来  我扶你们两个起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:28.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, let me help you two up
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.75,0:04:35.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天算是一场空
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:35.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, today was a wash
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.46,0:04:37.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是明天再来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:37.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guess I'll try again tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.71,0:04:40.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就只要睡上个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:40.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just need to sleep for
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.88,0:04:44.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,二十三小时半就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:44.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Twenty-three and a half hours
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.43,0:04:54.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有我这专利放屁床  保证你会是活宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.43,0:04:51.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll be the life of the slumber party
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:54.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with my patented whoopee bed
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.10,0:04:56.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别来烦我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.10,0:04:56.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.23,0:05:00.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有个橡皮梯子就是方便
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:05:00.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Always handy to have a rubber ladder
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.03,0:05:06.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.03,0:05:06.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here it is
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.03,0:05:10.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哒哒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:10.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ta-da
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.49,0:05:14.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样才叫快闪店
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.49,0:05:14.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, that's what I call a pop-up store
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.49,0:05:14.04,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1092,920)}弹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:18.92,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(622,332)}章爸的\N恶作剧商店
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.79,0:05:16.00,标准-Chi,,700,0,0,,快来参观
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.79,0:05:16.00,标准-Eng,,700,0,0,,Step right up to
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.00,0:05:18.58,标准-Chi,,700,0,0,,章爸的恶作剧商店
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:18.58,标准-Eng,,700,0,0,,Jeffy T's Prankwell Emporium
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.58,0:05:20.29,标准-Chi,,700,0,0,,我是恶作剧小贩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:20.29,标准-Eng,,700,0,0,,I'm a peddler of pranks
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.29,0:05:23.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,整活货郎  恶搞店主
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:23.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a giver of gags, a trader of tricks
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.34,0:05:24.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如有需要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:24.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You need it
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.38,0:05:27.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新奇小道具我差不多都有卖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:27.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I sell a novelty approximation of it
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.55,0:05:29.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你朋友会说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.55,0:05:29.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your friends will be saying
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.14,0:05:31.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好多恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:31.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Prank's a lot"
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.26,0:05:34.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我倒要说这恶作剧都是白费力气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.26,0:05:34.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm saying pranks for nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.81,0:05:37.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁能想得到章鱼哥的老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:37.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who would have thought Squidward's dad
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.40,0:05:39.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,居然会这么有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.40,0:05:39.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,would be such a lively guy?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.11,0:05:39.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:39.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.65,0:05:40.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他让我好想笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:40.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He makes me laugh
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.23,0:05:43.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章  章鱼哥反倒让我很难过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.23,0:05:43.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,S-Squidward just makes me sad
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.99,0:05:45.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胡说八道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.99,0:05:45.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nonsense
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.28,0:05:47.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥有自己的一套搞笑法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.28,0:05:47.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward is hilarious in his own right
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.36,0:05:49.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然他名叫章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.36,0:05:49.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, his name is Squidward
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.36,0:05:49.37,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1092,920)}鱿 鱼
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.37,0:05:51.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但他可是章鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.37,0:05:51.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but he's an octopus
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.83,0:05:53.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,简直就是我最棒的恶作剧之一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:53.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was one of my best pranks
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.00,0:05:56.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:05:56.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a good one
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.46,0:05:59.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能再看点你的新奇恶作剧吗  章先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:05:59.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can we see more of your novelty gags, Mr. Tentacles?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.46,0:06:01.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我儿子才那么叫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:01.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, Mr. Tentacles is my son
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.96,0:06:03.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,叫我章爸才对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.96,0:06:03.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Call me Jeffy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.01,0:06:10.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好东西还有不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.01,0:06:10.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's more where that came from
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.85,0:06:13.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是一点我的原型恶搞道具
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.85,0:06:13.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here are just a few of my prototype gags
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.89,0:06:15.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,斑点肥皂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.89,0:06:15.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Polka dot soap
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.73,0:06:18.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有点棒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.73,0:06:18.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dot's great
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.19,0:06:20.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,隐形鱿鱼墨水
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:20.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Disappearing squid ink
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.86,0:06:26.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤子钱可以省下不少了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:26.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Think of all the money I'll save on pants
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.03,0:06:28.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别忘了我的炸弹冰棍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.03,0:06:28.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And don't forget my bombsicles
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.03,0:06:34.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,酷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.03,0:06:34.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cool
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.49,0:06:35.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.49,0:06:35.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.16,0:06:38.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我职业生涯里开发出了几千样恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:37.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've developed thousands of gags
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:38.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,over the course of my career
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.79,0:06:40.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最近我还在研发
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:40.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've even been working on
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.92,0:06:43.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终极恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.92,0:06:43.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the ultimate gag
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.80,0:06:47.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过目前还没准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.80,0:06:47.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But it's just not ready yet
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.92,0:06:50.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,基本没什么头绪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.92,0:06:50.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't seem to figure it out
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.68,0:06:52.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们可以帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.68,0:06:52.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can help
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.80,0:06:53.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:53.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.43,0:06:56.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看你的新恶作剧  章爸哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.43,0:06:56.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Show us your new gags, Mr. Jeffyward
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.56,0:06:58.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是好主意  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.56,0:06:58.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Brilliant idea, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.73,0:07:02.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不你们来我测试厨房里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:07:02.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't you step into my test kitchen
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.90,0:07:05.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这地方看着好像章鱼哥家的厨房
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:05.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, this looks a lot like Squidward's kitchen
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.69,0:07:08.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当作我的恶搞实验室就行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:08.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Think of it as my gag lab
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.19,0:07:10.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在里面安插了我最新的几个恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.19,0:07:10.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've planted some of my newest pranks around
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.82,0:07:11.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比如说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.82,0:07:11.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For instance
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.58,0:07:15.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,米虫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.58,0:07:15.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rice lice
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.62,0:07:21.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总有几个谁厨艺巨烂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.62,0:07:21.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Some people are so bad at cooking
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.71,0:07:23.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连水都不会烧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.71,0:07:23.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,they can't even boil water
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.55,0:07:30.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,家里有烧火壶就更不会烧水了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:30.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Especially not with a flammable pot
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.38,0:07:33.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他得把烈火器给找来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.38,0:07:33.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He better grab that fire re-stinguisher
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.22,0:07:35.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给  儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:35.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, son
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.01,0:07:37.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用这朵喷射花
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.01,0:07:37.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Use this squirting flower
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.81,0:07:43.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这才是真正的灭火器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.81,0:07:43.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the real fire extinguisher
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.56,0:07:46.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起码火确实灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:46.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, at least the fire's out
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.57,0:07:50.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我动不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:50.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm stuck
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.90,0:07:52.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:52.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's because
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.86,0:07:55.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这也是方便面包
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:55.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's also instant bread
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.74,0:07:56.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哒哒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:56.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ta-da
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.29,0:08:01.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,趁热吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:01.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get it while it's hot
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.66,0:08:03.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是超火清仓大甩卖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.66,0:08:03.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a fire sale
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.87,0:08:05.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁想来买点乐子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.87,0:08:05.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, who wants to buy some fun?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.04,0:08:07.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:07.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.50,0:08:10.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要到没有乐子的地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:10.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going where there won't be any fun
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.76,0:08:12.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上班
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.76,0:08:12.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Work
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.84,0:08:14.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:14.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.68,0:08:15.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.68,0:08:15.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.06,0:08:19.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的眼角膜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:19.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My cornea
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.85,0:08:21.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这钱不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.85,0:08:21.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Something's wrong with this money
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.85,0:08:23.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好跟蟹老板报告一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.85,0:08:23.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I better go tell Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.89,0:08:24.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.89,0:08:24.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.77,0:08:27.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才不会去收拾那玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:27.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not cleaning that up
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.73,0:08:29.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.73,0:08:29.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.40,0:08:33.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你牙齿看着怎么比平常还诡异
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:33.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why do your teeth look weirder than usual?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.53,0:08:35.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,橡皮牙齿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.53,0:08:35.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rubber teeth
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.91,0:08:38.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个是橡皮落地食物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.91,0:08:38.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And this is a rubber spill
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.62,0:08:40.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有橡皮钱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:40.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And rubber money
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.66,0:08:42.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这些恶作剧道具都是找你爸买的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:42.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I bought all these pranks from your dad
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.75,0:08:44.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是很搞笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:44.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aren't they hilarious?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.21,0:08:46.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:46.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.83,0:08:49.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝又在讨人厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:49.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob is being obnoxious again
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.59,0:08:52.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,整到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:52.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Got ya
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.34,0:08:55.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是我举世闻名的橡皮老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.34,0:08:55.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's my famous rubber boss
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.72,0:08:57.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要九十九块九毛九
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:08:57.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For only 99.99
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.85,0:09:00.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我再也受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.85,0:09:00.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't take it anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.02,0:09:05.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:05.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.44,0:09:09.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你爸卖我这个巨型水气球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.44,0:09:09.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your dad sold me this giant water balloon
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.32,0:09:11.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才四十九块九毛九
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.32,0:09:11.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Only 49.99
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.98,0:09:12.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:12.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Catch
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.82,0:09:14.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.82,0:09:14.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.99,0:09:19.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,里面全是水母
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:19.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's full of jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.38,0:09:33.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在该做点我很早就该做的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:33.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now to do something I should've done a long time ago
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.01,0:09:38.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,漂亮的宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:38.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Beautiful baby
Dialogue: 1,0:09:39.60,0:09:41.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那么  我挚爱的老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.60,0:09:41.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, daddy dearest
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.51,0:09:43.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你喜欢恶作剧是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.51,0:09:43.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You like pranks, do ya?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.89,0:09:48.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我倒要给你点让你永生难忘的恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.89,0:09:48.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll give this some pranks you'll never forget
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.62,0:10:02.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.62,0:10:02.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Morning, son
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.83,0:10:04.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看着还是和平常一样活泼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.83,0:10:04.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looking chipper as always
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.54,0:10:07.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要送你一样礼物  老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.54,0:10:07.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have a present for you, Father
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.67,0:10:08.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,送我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:08.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For me?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.96,0:10:10.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没那必要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.96,0:10:10.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't have
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.42,0:10:14.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可你真该收下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.42,0:10:14.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But you really deserve it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.59,0:10:16.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道会是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.59,0:10:16.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wonder what it could be
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.18,0:10:20.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,惊喜拳击手套
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.18,0:10:20.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A surprise boxing glove?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.14,0:10:22.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我太爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:22.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.39,0:10:25.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有奶油派
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:25.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And a cream pie?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.81,0:10:28.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这奶油还是痒痒膏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.81,0:10:28.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With itching cream
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.48,0:10:33.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有臭屁弹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.48,0:10:33.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And a stink bomb too
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.00,0:10:51.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.00,0:10:51.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Son
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.08,0:10:52.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.08,0:10:52.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.21,0:10:54.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终极恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:54.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The ultimate gag
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.89,0:11:04.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别动我小指啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.89,0:11:04.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not my pinky
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.47,0:11:07.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很好笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.47,0:11:07.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pretty funny, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.06,0:11:11.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来玩到昏头昏脑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.06,0:11:11.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, knock yourselves out
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.40,0:11:12.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.40,0:11:12.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.36,0:11:21.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的的确确很像你老爸了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.36,0:11:21.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You certainly take after your old man
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.37,0:11:25.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我真为你骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:25.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm so proud of you
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.66,0:11:28.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你帮我做出了终极恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.66,0:11:28.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for figuring out my ultimate gag
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.75,0:11:31.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我能跟全世界共享了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:31.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I can share it with the world
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.08,0:11:36.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这就去打包行李  马上出发
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.08,0:11:36.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll just go pack up my things and head out
Dialogue: 1,0:11:36.96,0:11:37.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:37.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.88,0:11:41.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就想听你这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:41.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's all I ever wanted to hear you say
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.85,0:11:45.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,整到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:45.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Got ya
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:51.23,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\fsp45\c&H00FFB5&}舌尖上的\N{\fs30} \N{\fs175}痞老板
