Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:12:01.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(938,794)}海之霸
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.36,0:12:04.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在回到  海洋恶心生物世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:04.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now back to The World of Gross Sea Life
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.66,0:12:04.62,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1030,342)}海洋恶心生物\N世界
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.03,0:12:07.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看这机敏的等足类寄生虫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.03,0:12:07.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Observe how this ingenious parasitic isopod
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.74,0:12:14.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,附在鱼嘴里化为舌头  找到了新家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.74,0:12:10.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,finds a new home by attaching itself
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.54,0:12:14.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,inside a fish's mouth, becoming its new tongue
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.29,0:12:21.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是我见过最恶心的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.29,0:12:21.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's the most disgusting thing I've ever seen
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.38,0:12:26.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既恶心又天才
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.38,0:12:26.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Disgustingly genius
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.14,0:12:29.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我想到了个绝佳好办法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.14,0:12:29.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's giving me a wonderful idea
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.06,0:12:32.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要把自己粘到海绵宝宝的舌头上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:32.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll glue myself to SpongeBob's tongue
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.64,0:12:35.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要躲在那煎炸厨师的脸上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.64,0:12:35.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,By hiding right in that fry cook's face
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.60,0:12:40.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就可以刚刚好采样到一份蟹黄堡了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.60,0:12:37.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll be in the perfect position
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.86,0:12:40.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to collect a Krabby Patty sample
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.20,0:12:50.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么可能会出错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.20,0:12:50.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, what could possibly go wrong?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.79,0:12:54.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,巧妙的伪装
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.79,0:12:54.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Clever disguise?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.16,0:12:54.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.16,0:12:54.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Check
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.04,0:12:56.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,采样容器
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:12:56.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sample container?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.38,0:12:57.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.38,0:12:57.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Check
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.38,0:12:58.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胶水
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.38,0:12:58.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Glue?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.38,0:12:58.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.38,0:12:58.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Check
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.30,0:13:03.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在启动压迫舌头行动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.30,0:13:03.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to begin operation tongue oppressor
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.47,0:13:11.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一天一熨斗  保证没褶皱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.47,0:13:11.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,An iron a day keeps the wrinkles away
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.19,0:13:17.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望来的是推销员
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.19,0:13:17.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hope it's a salesman
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.73,0:13:19.36,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 附有问候或其它写就信息的一盒糖果 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.73,0:13:19.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蜜糖传书
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.73,0:13:19.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Candy-gram
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.19,0:13:23.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就爱听蜜糖传即兴诗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.19,0:13:23.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just love a Poetry-Slam Candy-gram
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.94,0:13:25.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,即兴诗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.94,0:13:25.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Poetry?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.03,0:13:26.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.03,0:13:26.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, okay
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.61,0:13:29.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,玫瑰是红的  糖果是甜的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:29.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Roses are red, candy is sweet
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.37,0:13:33.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃糖要用嘴  千万别用脚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.37,0:13:33.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eat with your mouth, not with your feet?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.46,0:13:36.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好个生活小忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.46,0:13:36.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Words to live by
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.55,0:13:43.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就对了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.55,0:13:43.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.84,0:13:46.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快吃下甜甜的小痞老板吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.84,0:13:46.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eat the delicious little plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.72,0:13:48.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只吃一小颗糖果就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.72,0:13:48.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll just have one little candy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.51,0:13:53.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我逗谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.51,0:13:53.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who am I kidding?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.23,0:13:58.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快啊  你个白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:13:58.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, you dolt
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.10,0:13:59.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快吃我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:13:59.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eat me
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.57,0:14:05.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这颗粉红色的糖果看着就挺好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.57,0:14:05.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This pink candy looks so delicious
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.86,0:14:08.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.86,0:14:08.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.74,0:14:10.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我要把它留给你吃  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.74,0:14:10.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That I saved it just for you, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.21,0:14:27.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我非要进那个傻子的嘴巴不可
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.21,0:14:27.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have to get inside that mouth breather's mouth
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.67,0:14:30.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许得把自己伪装成上门牙医
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.67,0:14:30.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe disguise myself as a door to door dentist?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.22,0:14:32.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好像没那种牙医
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.22,0:14:32.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, that's not a thing
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.27,0:14:36.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我踩着陈年口香糖了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.27,0:14:36.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I stepped in some old gum
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.62,0:15:00.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在把自己粘到他的丑舌头上就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,0:15:00.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now, I just have to glue myself to his hideous tongue
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.29,0:15:05.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.29,0:15:05.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.22,0:15:10.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.22,0:15:10.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.30,0:15:16.97,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1534,514)}拗口\N绕口令\N小册
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.56,0:15:16.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拗口绕口令小册
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.56,0:15:16.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"The Tiny Book of Tortuous Tongue Twisters"
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.22,0:15:19.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿来晨练刚刚好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:19.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perfect for my morning exercises
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.52,0:15:22.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我舌头得状态良好才能吃蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:22.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My tongue has to be in tip top shape to taste my patties
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.48,0:15:24.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绕口令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.48,0:15:24.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tongue twisters?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.15,0:15:26.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怪鳕小队
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:26.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"The squad of odd cod
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.36,0:15:29.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鼓掌欢迎轻狂头足类
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.36,0:15:29.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,applaud the sassy cephalopod"
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.24,0:15:30.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,疼死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.24,0:15:30.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The pain
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.36,0:15:33.41,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(532,270)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.70,0:15:36.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奇计顺利已在即
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:36.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This dream scheme gone full steam
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.24,0:15:38.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尤金必定惊爆鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.24,0:15:38.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,guarantees Eugene's screams
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.41,0:15:40.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.41,0:15:40.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.25,0:15:41.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拗到我口了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.25,0:15:41.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, I'm doing it
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.83,0:15:44.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.83,0:15:44.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Morning, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.97,0:15:55.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你口气有股海霸糊味
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:55.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your breath smells like chum
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.89,0:16:02.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实有点臭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.89,0:16:02.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is a bit stinky
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.11,0:16:07.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你穿越蜗牛的肠道试试
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.11,0:16:07.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You try passing through a snail's intestines
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.36,0:16:09.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看你有多香
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.36,0:16:09.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and see what you smell like
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.23,0:16:11.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喷点口气清新剂应该就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.23,0:16:11.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A little breath spray should help
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.49,0:16:20.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来搬出冰库的肉饼  准备今天的餐点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:19.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Better get some patties out of the freezer
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.29,0:16:20.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for today's orders
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.50,0:16:24.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.50,0:16:24.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.54,0:16:26.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肉饼用光了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.54,0:16:26.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're out of patties
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.63,0:16:28.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还真是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:28.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course, you are
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.25,0:16:31.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我可以再做新一批肉饼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.25,0:16:31.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Which means I get to make a whole new batch
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.30,0:16:32.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:32.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.59,0:16:35.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还更好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.59,0:16:35.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Even better
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.09,0:16:38.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以坐前排观赏全过程了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.09,0:16:38.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll have a front-row seat to the whole process
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.93,0:16:44.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一点机密食材A
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.93,0:16:44.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A little secret ingredient A
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.31,0:16:46.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,机密食材A
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.31,0:16:46.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Secret ingredient A?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.40,0:16:50.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两团B
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.40,0:16:50.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Two plops of B
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.90,0:16:55.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一点CDE还有G
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.90,0:16:55.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Some C, D, E, and G
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.99,0:16:58.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两杯这个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.99,0:16:58.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Two cups of this
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.16,0:16:59.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一罐那个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.16,0:16:59.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A jar of that
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.87,0:17:02.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再加一小撮Z
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.87,0:17:02.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And just a pinch of Z
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.08,0:17:04.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这家伙在做什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.08,0:17:04.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's this guy making?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.16,0:17:05.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,字母汤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.16,0:17:05.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Alphabet soup?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.87,0:17:06.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拌匀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.87,0:17:06.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mix well
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.42,0:17:12.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完美
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.42,0:17:12.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perfect
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.34,0:17:13.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来试试口味
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.34,0:17:13.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now for the taste test
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.59,0:17:15.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就对了  宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.59,0:17:15.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it, baby
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.22,0:17:17.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要一份样本就行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.22,0:17:17.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I only need one sample
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.64,0:17:22.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.64,0:17:22.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My eye
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.14,0:17:25.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这肉饼有点没味道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:25.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These patties are kind of bland
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.44,0:17:27.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尝不了一点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:27.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't taste them at all
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.15,0:17:29.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来发挥一点点创意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:29.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to get a little creative
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.77,0:17:31.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加点林堡奶酪应该就有味道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:31.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe some Limburger cheese will help
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.65,0:17:33.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.65,0:17:33.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.74,0:17:35.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别加林堡奶酪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.74,0:17:35.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not Limburger
Dialogue: 1,0:17:42.62,0:17:44.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是没味
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:44.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Still blah
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.45,0:17:46.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就来加一点德国酸菜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.45,0:17:46.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about a little sauerkraut?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.87,0:17:48.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,飞天魔鬼辣椒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.87,0:17:48.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Flying Dutchman peppers
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.46,0:17:50.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有他的陈年足垢罐头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.46,0:17:50.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And this old jar of toe jam
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.05,0:17:54.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海神王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.05,0:17:54.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good, Neptune
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.88,0:17:56.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别吃进你嘴里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:17:56.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not in your mouth
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.47,0:18:06.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是一点味道都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.47,0:18:06.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Still doesn't have any taste
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.64,0:18:09.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来我犯了个天大的错误
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.64,0:18:09.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've made a critical error
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.77,0:18:13.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我胶水把那傻子的味蕾给盖住了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.77,0:18:13.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My glue has covered that dolt's taste buds
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.15,0:18:15.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,动作快点  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.15,0:18:15.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get a move on, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.19,0:18:16.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,点餐单都快堆成山了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:16.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The orders are piling up
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.78,0:18:18.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没问题  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.78,0:18:18.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No problem, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.03,0:18:20.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来只能凑合用了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.03,0:18:20.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess it'll have to do
Dialogue: 1,0:18:21.41,0:18:23.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡都准备好了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.41,0:18:23.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Krabby Patties are ready, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.41,0:18:24.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,随你便
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.41,0:18:24.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whatever
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.04,0:18:28.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢海神王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:28.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank Neptune
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.37,0:18:30.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都饿坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.37,0:18:30.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm starving
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.13,0:18:31.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总算来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.13,0:18:31.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Finally
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.92,0:18:36.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这还是吃的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.92,0:18:36.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is this even food?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.26,0:18:45.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恶心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.26,0:18:45.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is disgusting
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.64,0:18:49.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再也不来这吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.64,0:18:49.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll never eat here again
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.69,0:18:51.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还吃过更好吃的垃圾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.69,0:18:51.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've had better garbage
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.61,0:18:53.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比海霸糊还难吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.61,0:18:53.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It tastes worse than chum
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.19,0:18:58.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比海霸糊难吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.19,0:18:58.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Worse than chum?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:06.58,0:19:09.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你把我蟹黄堡怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.58,0:19:09.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What have you done to my patties?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.79,0:19:15.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:15.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.50,0:19:17.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡今天一点味道都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.50,0:19:17.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The patties have no flavor at all today
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.76,0:19:18.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没味道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.76,0:19:18.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No flavor?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.97,0:19:21.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,味道太重了才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.97,0:19:21.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,More like too much flavor
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.05,0:19:23.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,简直跟飞天魔鬼的长内裤一个味
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.05,0:19:23.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They taste like the Flying Dutchman's long johns
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.01,0:19:28.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的味蕾恐怕已经劳累过度了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.01,0:19:28.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid your taste buds are worn out, boy-o
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.23,0:19:31.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你舌头没康复
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.23,0:19:31.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Until your tongue recovers
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.85,0:19:33.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就先别做蟹黄堡了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.85,0:19:33.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you're off grill duty
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.44,0:19:35.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把帽子跟锅铲交上来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.44,0:19:35.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Turn in your hat and spatula
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.99,0:19:47.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这回又失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.99,0:19:47.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's one more for the failure pile
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.91,0:19:49.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该弃舌逃命了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.91,0:19:49.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to abandon tongue
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.63,0:19:56.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.63,0:19:56.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Blast
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.59,0:19:58.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拉链被胶水粘住了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.59,0:19:58.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The zipper's covered in glue
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.34,0:20:04.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我左边胳肢窝的声音还是有点尖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.34,0:20:04.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My left armpit still sounds a little sharp
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.52,0:20:11.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好听多了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.52,0:20:11.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's better
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.35,0:20:13.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.35,0:20:13.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.44,0:20:14.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.44,0:20:14.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.90,0:20:16.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.90,0:20:16.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.19,0:20:18.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我尝不出味道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.19,0:20:18.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't taste a thing
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.57,0:20:20.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我舌头坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.57,0:20:20.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My tongue is broken
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.49,0:20:23.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他居然会去请教派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.49,0:20:23.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He goes to Patrick for advice?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.03,0:20:25.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好个先傻带动后傻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.03,0:20:25.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the nitwits leading the dimwits
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.32,0:20:27.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你舌头很可能就只是脏了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.32,0:20:27.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your tongue's probably just dirty
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.45,0:20:29.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就老是那样子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.45,0:20:29.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That happens to me all the time
Dialogue: 1,0:20:33.04,0:20:35.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你简直是史上最聪明的大聪明了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:35.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're the smartest smart person who ever smarted
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.92,0:20:38.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奏个决胜曲吧  音乐大师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.92,0:20:38.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me a little run off music, maestro
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.76,0:20:47.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海神王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:47.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sweet Neptune
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.14,0:20:49.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.14,0:20:49.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.32,0:20:59.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得要强力点的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.32,0:20:59.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need something stronger
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.82,0:21:03.15,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1422,240)}洗船场
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.90,0:21:03.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个应该就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.90,0:21:03.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This should do the trick
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.04,0:21:15.79,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1208,746)}当心热蜡
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.26,0:21:27.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你帽子能借用一下吗  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.26,0:21:27.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,May I borrow your hat, sir?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.39,0:21:29.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然能了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.39,0:21:29.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.93,0:21:33.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,味道分外空虚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.93,0:21:33.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It tastes like emptiness
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.69,0:21:38.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我觉得味道还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.69,0:21:38.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tastes fine to me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.44,0:21:43.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可怜的舌头劳累过度了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.44,0:21:43.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My poor tongue is just worn out
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.44,0:21:46.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来该换条新舌头了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.44,0:21:46.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guess it's time for a new one
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.11,0:21:47.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.11,0:21:47.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.92,0:21:59.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可真傻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.92,0:21:59.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Silly me
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.09,0:22:01.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我咋没早点这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.09,0:22:01.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why didn't I do this earlier?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.84,0:22:07.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能借你那条肮脏的旧舌头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.84,0:22:07.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I borrow that dirty old tongue of yours?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.55,0:22:08.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.55,0:22:08.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.26,0:22:13.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星吃蟹黄堡吃得比谁都多
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.26,0:22:13.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick eats more Krabby Patties than anyone
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.81,0:22:16.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我咋没早点这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.81,0:22:16.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why didn't I do this earlier?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.19,0:22:19.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  我的旧舌头有点吵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.19,0:22:19.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, my old tongue's a little loud
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.31,0:22:20.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.31,0:22:20.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's okay
Dialogue: 1,0:22:24.36,0:22:25.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚刚好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.36,0:22:25.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perfect
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.44,0:22:27.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要去随便吃点东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.44,0:22:27.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm just gonna go grab a bite to eat
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.99,0:22:31.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到一年一度海霸大胃王比赛大吃特吃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.99,0:22:31.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,at the annual Chum Eating Contest
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.78,0:22:31.53,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(626,140)}海霸大胃王比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.78,0:22:31.53,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1594,278)}大奖
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.83,0:22:33.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海霸大胃王比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.83,0:22:33.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Chum eating contest?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:33.91,0:22:35.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天就办吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.91,0:22:35.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Was that today?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:35.37,0:22:36.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.37,0:22:36.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,On your marks
Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.29,0:22:38.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,预备
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.29,0:22:38.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,get set
Dialogue: 1,0:22:38.75,0:22:40.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海霸糊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.75,0:22:40.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,chum
Dialogue: 1,0:22:44.05,0:22:47.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凭什么我就没法有个可拆卸的舌头
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.05,0:22:47.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why can't I have a detachable tongue?
